intent: Menadione Phase 0 dose-response calibration - Template A

template.description: Pre-randomized template A for variance partitioning

design_goals: Establish Menadione dose-response curve for A549 cells
Quantify variance components (passage, plate, position, timepoint)
Provide power for detecting 10% viability differences
Fixed sentinel positions for cross-plate SPC
Randomized experimental positions for position effect averaging
